    {
      "id": "chunk:277040a098ae143a",
      "text": "A snapshot of the talented students in our MS in Applied Data Science program.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:d414377430ab1091",
      "text": "I chose the MS-ADS program for its rigorous, industry-focused curriculum and the opportunity to learn from world-class faculty who bridge academic research with real-world applications. The program’s emphasis on hands-on learning through the capstone project particularly appealed to me, as it allows students to tackle complex, data-driven problems in collaboration with leading organizations.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students"
      ],
      "source_type": "span"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:ef4b75be43e0f8ef",
      "text": "The MS in Applied Data Science program attracts learners at different stages of their academic and professional journeys. This chart compares age distribution across the Autumn 2025 in-person and online cohorts.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Age Breakdown (In-Person & Online)"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:b5ef77d04368995e",
      "text": "Our students come from a broad range of backgrounds and experiences. Below is a comparison of gender representation across the Autumn 2025 in-person and online cohorts.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Gender Breakdown (In-Person & Online)"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:2f45e6c415662eae",
      "text": "I chose this program due to a combination of theoretical learning and great connections to industry through the capstone project, events, and great alumni network.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:4c01d7568e7b47b5",
      "text": "Students enter the program with varied professional backgrounds—from early-career analysts to seasoned engineers and managers. This comparison shows the level of work experience represented in the Autumn 2025 in-person and online cohorts.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Work Experience (In-Person & Online)"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:193a8f9ebc6c8403",
      "text": "Our students come from a wide range of academic foundations. The charts below highlight the most common undergraduate majors represented in the Autumn 2025 in-person and online cohorts.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Top 5 Undergraduate Majors (In-Person & Online)"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:9c81ce61374db591",
      "text": "The Autumn 2025 in-person cohort includes students from around the world. This map highlights the primary citizenship of students in this incoming class.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Primary Citizenship (In-Person Students)"
      ],
      "source_type": "p"
    },
    {
      "id": "chunk:04069ba2fdc25939",
      "text": "I ultimately chose the MS-ADS program because I liked how experienced the professors were in the industry. I also appreciate that we are taught necessary skills that are very relevant to today’s job market in analytics, which I didn’t get to experience in undergrad.",
      "url": "https://datascience.uchicago.edu/education/masters-programs/ms-in-applied-data-science/our-students",
      "page_id": "page:1c2b530a9935e8fd",
      "page_title": "Our Students",
      "path": [
        "Our Students",
        "Meet a Few of Our Students",
        "Primary Citizenship (In-Person Students)"
      ],
      "source_type": "span"
    }
